Eggshells have calcium.

323
00:19:24,834 --> 00:19:25,876
Do you want some?

324
00:19:27,876 --> 00:19:29,125
I'm not sharing it with you.

325
00:19:29,250 --> 00:19:31,000
This was cooked by the woman I love.

326
00:19:34,834 --> 00:19:35,626
It's good.

327
00:19:35,751 --> 00:19:36,751
It's really good.

328
00:19:44,999 --> 00:19:45,999
Grandma.

329
00:19:46,667 --> 00:19:49,626
Yueshan is practicing her dancing right now.

330
00:19:51,542 --> 00:19:52,792
Are you sure

331
00:19:53,250 --> 00:19:55,959
you don't want to tell her about Ms. Siou'e's fall?

332
00:19:55,999 --> 00:19:57,459
Siou'e told us not to say anything.

333
00:19:57,751 --> 00:19:59,000
Then we shouldn't mention it.

334
00:20:00,667 --> 00:20:02,667
Ms. Siou'e dotes on Yueshan the most.

335
00:20:02,999 --> 00:20:03,999
I know.

336
00:20:04,500 --> 00:20:06,459
But she doesn't want Yueshan to worry.

337
00:20:07,959 --> 00:20:09,918
By the way, how is Yinmo doing?

338
00:20:09,999 --> 00:20:10,999
Is he okay?

339
00:20:11,292 --> 00:20:12,417
He's not doing well.

340
00:20:12,709 --> 00:20:14,626
There are paparazzi everywhere

341
00:20:14,999 --> 00:20:17,626
and the news is full of negative stories about him.

342
00:20:18,876 --> 00:20:20,584
Although he pretends not to care

343
00:20:22,209 --> 00:20:23,999
and he's trying hard to host us,

344
00:20:24,000 --> 00:20:25,000
it's just...

345
00:20:26,459 --> 00:20:27,459
Nuonuo.

346
00:20:27,999 --> 00:20:29,959
It has been a long time since you went to Taipei.

347
00:20:30,125 --> 00:20:32,375
There's no need to rush back this time.

348
00:20:33,334 --> 00:20:34,709
Dawu will take care of me.

349
00:20:35,667 --> 00:20:37,292
You just stay with Yinmo.

350
00:20:38,292 --> 00:20:40,000
His circle is quite complicated.

351
00:20:40,918 --> 00:20:41,999
With you by his side,

352
00:20:42,709 --> 00:20:44,125
he won't feel alone.

353
00:20:45,125 --> 00:20:46,667
Recently, the famous actor Bai Yinmo

354
00:20:46,792 --> 00:20:47,999
who was accused of assaulting a TV host,

355
00:20:48,000 --> 00:20:50,998
recently filmed a reality show on an outlying island.

356
00:20:50,999 --> 00:20:52,876
His mom made a surprise appearance,

357
00:20:52,999 --> 00:20:55,584
but Bai Yinmo stormed off angrily.

358
00:20:55,709 --> 00:20:56,751
It also led to...

359
00:21:26,834 --> 00:21:27,834
What are you doing?

360
00:21:31,999 --> 00:21:32,999
I'm drawing.

361
00:21:37,083 --> 00:21:38,083
I can't sleep.

362
00:21:43,083 --> 00:21:45,542
Is it because of the negative news?

363
00:21:54,999 --> 00:21:56,999
I'll meet with my agent tomorrow

364
00:21:57,999 --> 00:21:59,119
to figure out the situation.

365
00:22:04,209 --> 00:22:06,083
Is there anything I can do to help?

366
00:22:16,000 --> 00:22:18,417
You've already helped me.

367
00:22:21,542 --> 00:22:23,834
At least I'll be able to sleep well tonight.

368
00:22:25,000 --> 00:22:26,000
Also,

369
00:22:26,999 --> 00:22:29,079
thank you for the special sleeping pill from Kinmen.

370
00:22:29,626 --> 00:22:30,626
They are very sweet.

371
00:22:32,959 --> 00:22:33,999
Did you just realize?

372
00:22:37,125 --> 00:22:39,250
Don't eat too many at once.

373
00:22:39,375 --> 00:22:40,615
Otherwise, you'll get cavities.

374
00:23:14,500 --> 00:23:15,292
Ms. Shuman.

375
00:23:15,417 --> 00:23:16,209
Coming.

376
00:23:16,334 --> 00:23:17,334
We're heading out now.

377
00:23:17,375 --> 00:23:18,375
Okay.

378
00:23:19,999 --> 00:23:22,626
You're finally willing to go out with me.

379
00:23:22,751 --> 00:23:25,292
You're always looking out for me even though you're so busy.

380
00:23:25,417 --> 00:23:26,998
I feel bad.

381
00:23:26,999 --> 00:23:28,792
What's there to feel bad about?

382
00:23:28,918 --> 00:23:30,125
I'm like your grandson.

383
00:23:31,834 --> 00:23:32,834
Dawu.

384
00:23:33,209 --> 00:23:35,999
I know how you feel about Nuonuo.

385
00:23:36,667 --> 00:23:37,999
But don't worry.

386
00:23:38,000 --> 00:23:40,334
Fate will guide someone

387
00:23:40,459 --> 00:23:42,584
who's perfect for you to cross your path.

388
00:23:44,542 --> 00:23:45,998
Right now, the most perfect one for me

389
00:23:45,999 --> 00:23:47,626
is you.

390
00:23:47,751 --> 00:23:49,417
So from now on, you have to listen to me.

391
00:23:49,542 --> 00:23:50,918
When I ask you to go out with me,

392
00:23:50,999 --> 00:23:52,959
you can't say no anymore, okay?

393
00:23:52,999 --> 00:23:53,999
Okay.

394
00:23:54,334 --> 00:23:55,667
I'll listen to you.

395
00:24:00,250 --> 00:24:01,250
Did you get anything?

396
00:24:01,459 --> 00:24:02,459
No, I didn't.

397
00:24:07,167 --> 00:24:08,167
Wait.

398
00:24:16,375 --> 00:24:17,542
Here they come.

399
00:25:43,834 --> 00:25:45,292
What's his problem?

400
00:25:46,042 --> 00:25:47,667
Why does he keep taking the same route?

401
00:25:49,542 --> 00:25:50,542
It's fine.

402
00:25:50,999 --> 00:25:51,999
Just keep following him.

403
00:26:01,000 --> 00:26:02,042
Thank you.

404
00:26:02,167 --> 00:26:03,667
- Bye. - Bye.

405
00:26:07,125 --> 00:26:08,393
Are you sure you don't want me to give you a ride?

406
00:26:08,417 --> 00:26:09,626
No need, Master.

407
00:26:10,125 --> 00:26:11,125
There's no MRT in Kinmen,

408
00:26:11,250 --> 00:26:12,850
so we wanted to experience it in Taipei.

409
00:26:13,417 --> 00:26:14,417
Thank you, Master.

410
00:26:14,876 --> 00:26:15,876
We'll be fine.

411
00:26:16,999 --> 00:26:17,999
Tang Mi.

412
00:26:18,667 --> 00:26:19,667
Thank you.

413
00:26:28,083 --> 00:26:29,083
Thank you.

414
00:26:30,375 --> 00:26:31,876
- Bye then. - Bye.

415
00:26:37,876 --> 00:26:38,876
Thank you.

416
00:26:39,999 --> 00:26:42,125
This is what a scandalous girlfriend should do.

417
00:26:42,999 --> 00:26:44,879
I should be doing better than Xiaoguang, right?

418
00:26:45,375 --> 00:26:47,042
It's hard to do worse than him.

419
00:26:49,792 --> 00:26:51,459
I called your mom this morning.

420
00:26:51,834 --> 00:26:52,999
She said she's fine.

421
00:26:53,334 --> 00:26:55,584
She wasn't recognized or bothered.

422
00:26:55,751 --> 00:26:56,751
Don't worry.

423
00:26:57,459 --> 00:26:59,042
Once everything calms down,

424
00:26:59,250 --> 00:27:00,584
I'll take her home.

425
00:27:25,000 --> 00:27:26,292
Is that it?

426
00:27:34,459 --> 00:27:35,751
Is Bai Yinmo too bored or what?

427
00:27:35,876 --> 00:27:37,999
- Is he crazy? - Why is he going in circles?

428
00:27:40,959 --> 00:27:41,959
Forget it.

429
00:27:42,626 --> 00:27:44,999
We won't get any updates by staying here.

430
00:27:45,834 --> 00:27:46,954
Let's go chase another lead.

431
00:27:50,709 --> 00:27:51,709
Hey.

432
00:27:52,542 --> 00:27:54,582
They've all left. Are you still going to stay here?

433
00:27:55,626 --> 00:27:56,417
Of course.

434
00:27:56,542 --> 00:27:57,822
I'm not going back empty-handed.

435
00:27:59,751 --> 00:28:01,471
We'll definitely catch him if we wait here.

436
00:28:18,334 --> 00:28:20,876
This is what you gave me

437
00:28:20,999 --> 00:28:22,479
when you won your first acting award.

438
00:28:23,792 --> 00:28:26,999
At the time, I didn't think you could act.

439
00:28:27,709 --> 00:28:29,167
I just wanted you to give it a try.

440
00:28:30,626 --> 00:28:32,999
I didn't expect you to really surprise me.

441
00:28:33,834 --> 00:28:36,667
You lost 7 kg for a minor role.

442
00:28:37,083 --> 00:28:38,459
You even won an award.

443
00:28:41,417 --> 00:28:42,709
Best Supporting Actor.

444
00:28:42,834 --> 00:28:43,834
Best Actor.

445
00:28:43,959 --> 00:28:44,999
Popularity Award.

446
00:28:48,292 --> 00:28:50,667
You gave me every single trophy.

447
00:28:53,626 --> 00:28:55,459
Through every sleepless night and tough day,

448
00:28:56,999 --> 00:28:58,999
I owe it to them for always being by my side.

449
00:29:06,209 --> 00:29:08,000
I'm here to hear your explanation.

450
00:29:10,834 --> 00:29:12,999
Everyone is waiting for me to give an explanation.

451
00:29:15,999 --> 00:29:17,626
How should I explain it?

452
00:29:29,250 --> 00:29:30,918
An agent betrayed their artist

453
00:29:31,375 --> 00:29:32,709
for the sake of the company.

454
00:29:35,667 --> 00:29:37,347
You arranged for my mom to be on the show.

455
00:29:37,999 --> 00:29:39,639
Those shareholders made you do it, right?

456
00:29:43,834 --> 00:29:45,542
From your DUI to the assault incident,

457
00:29:47,167 --> 00:29:49,792
the major shareholder has been threatening me

458
00:29:50,292 --> 00:29:52,042
to hand the company over to someone else.

459
00:29:52,167 --> 00:29:54,999
Even though I arranged Tang Mi to join the reality show,

460
00:29:55,042 --> 00:29:56,209
he still wasn't satisfied.

461
00:29:59,999 --> 00:30:03,167
I had no choice but to go to your mom.

462
00:30:06,667 --> 00:30:07,751
I know

463
00:30:09,626 --> 00:30:10,999
those are just excuses.

464
00:30:12,709 --> 00:30:14,709
Did you ever consider that I might refuse to film?

465
00:30:16,000 --> 00:30:17,000
Of course I did.

466
00:30:17,918 --> 00:30:19,292
I warned the major shareholder,

467
00:30:19,918 --> 00:30:21,417
but he didn't care at all.

468
00:30:22,584 --> 00:30:24,042
He didn't mind sacrificing you.

469
00:30:27,209 --> 00:30:28,751
He only cares about the traffic.

470
00:30:31,999 --> 00:30:32,999
Well, they've succeeded.

471
00:30:33,751 --> 00:30:34,751
Yes.

472
00:30:35,459 --> 00:30:36,667
The buzz is building.

473
00:30:38,167 --> 00:30:39,967
They're already discussing the second season.

474
00:30:43,083 --> 00:30:44,083
So...

475
00:30:45,999 --> 00:30:47,999
at least your company is safe, right?

476
00:30:52,792 --> 00:30:54,834
The major shareholder called me this morning.

477
00:30:55,999 --> 00:30:58,584
He said I have to take responsibility and hand over the company.

478
00:31:01,709 --> 00:31:02,709
I guess

479
00:31:03,334 --> 00:31:05,534
he has been wanting to take over the company all along.

480
00:31:07,834 --> 00:31:08,999
He has been using me.

481
00:31:16,918 --> 00:31:17,918
Yinmo.

482
00:31:20,542 --> 00:31:22,042
I've let you down.

483
00:31:27,959 --> 00:31:29,000
I've taken all your honors

484
00:31:30,918 --> 00:31:31,999
for too long.

485
00:31:33,999 --> 00:31:35,599
It's time to return them to their owner.

486
00:31:47,125 --> 00:31:48,167
You can keep them.

487
00:31:48,292 --> 00:31:49,292
I don't need them.

488
00:32:24,999 --> 00:32:25,999
All right. Thank you.

489
00:32:26,042 --> 00:32:27,042
That's all for now.

490
00:32:28,459 --> 00:32:29,542
Dawu.

491
00:32:29,667 --> 00:32:30,959
Don't tell Nuonuo, okay?

492
00:32:32,125 --> 00:32:33,834
Ms. Shuman, you're overreacting.

493
00:32:33,959 --> 00:32:35,159
I was dealing with work stuff.

494
00:32:36,459 --> 00:32:37,250
Sorry.

495
00:32:37,375 --> 00:32:38,375
I misunderstood.

496
00:32:39,459 --> 00:32:40,334
Ms. Shuman.

497
00:32:40,459 --> 00:32:42,792
Should we tell Hainuo about it?

498
00:32:42,918 --> 00:32:44,584
If we don't tell her,

499
00:32:44,709 --> 00:32:45,998
she'll definitely scold me.

500
00:32:45,999 --> 00:32:47,751
No. Don't tell her.

501
00:32:48,626 --> 00:32:51,375
It's just a stent for my heart.

502
00:32:51,834 --> 00:32:53,998
Let her stay in Taipei without worrying.

503
00:32:53,999 --> 00:32:55,399
We'll tell her when she comes back.

504
00:32:56,751 --> 00:32:58,584
I'm at ease with you around.

505
00:33:00,626 --> 00:33:01,626
Fine.

506
00:33:01,667 --> 00:33:03,417
I really can't do anything about you.

507
00:33:03,542 --> 00:33:04,918
Let's go back.

508
00:33:04,999 --> 00:33:05,999
Let's go.

509
00:33:06,292 --> 00:33:07,292
Come on.

510
00:33:09,999 --> 00:33:11,250
Where is this?

511
00:33:12,542 --> 00:33:14,662
We've been walking forever since getting off the bus.

512
00:33:16,417 --> 00:33:18,792
I think the old man gave us the wrong address.

513
00:33:24,167 --> 00:33:25,334
Looks like we're here.

514
00:33:26,292 --> 00:33:27,292
We're here.

515
00:33:27,792 --> 00:33:28,999
This is a construction site.

516
00:33:30,999 --> 00:33:32,792
- Da. - Yes, sir.

517
00:33:32,999 --> 00:33:34,083
Put these over here.

518
00:33:34,209 --> 00:33:35,584
There are some more over there.

519
00:33:35,709 --> 00:33:37,334
Use the cart to bring them over, okay?

520
00:33:37,459 --> 00:33:38,584
Yes, sir.

521
00:34:24,667 --> 00:34:25,667
Jingliang.

522
00:34:25,999 --> 00:34:26,959
- Thank you. - Have some water.

523
00:34:26,999 --> 00:34:27,876
No problem.

524
00:34:27,999 --> 00:34:28,792
Rest for a while.

525
00:34:28,918 --> 00:34:29,918
Okay.

526
00:34:39,000 --> 00:34:39,999
Yueshan.

527
00:34:39,999 --> 00:34:40,999
Have some water.

528
00:34:42,626 --> 00:34:45,083
Why didn't you let me know before coming over?

529
00:34:45,209 --> 00:34:46,999
I could've taken leave earlier.

530
00:34:47,999 --> 00:34:48,792
Never mind.

531
00:34:48,918 --> 00:34:50,393
I'll ask the boss for a half day off.

532
00:34:50,417 --> 00:34:53,998
Later, I'll take you and Jingliang out for a nice meal.

533
00:34:53,999 --> 00:34:55,584
Give me a minute to apply for leave.

534
00:34:57,334 --> 00:34:58,959
Why didn't you go back home?

535
00:35:04,792 --> 00:35:06,250
Did you forget about me and Grandma?

536
00:35:20,751 --> 00:35:22,042
Of course I didn't.

537
00:35:22,167 --> 00:35:23,792
How could I forget you?

538
00:35:26,999 --> 00:35:28,918
Why aren't you working at the tea shop anymore?

539
00:35:32,375 --> 00:35:35,250
Honestly, I'm not that into tea.

540
00:35:35,959 --> 00:35:39,792
Moreover, after being around tea lovers for so long,

541
00:35:39,918 --> 00:35:40,918
I got tired of it.

542
00:35:41,375 --> 00:35:42,417
I'm exhausted.

543
00:35:43,125 --> 00:35:45,751
This new environment is pretty good for me.

544
00:35:45,876 --> 00:35:48,167
My colleagues and friends here are all great.

545
00:35:48,292 --> 00:35:50,834
We're happy every day

546
00:35:50,999 --> 00:35:52,417
and time just flies by.

547
00:35:52,584 --> 00:35:53,959
So don't worry, Yueshan.

548
00:35:53,999 --> 00:35:55,375
I'm doing fine here.

549
00:35:55,667 --> 00:35:56,667
I can handle it.

550
00:35:59,959 --> 00:36:01,719
You should've told us that you changed jobs.

551
00:36:08,751 --> 00:36:09,751
After all,

552
00:36:10,959 --> 00:36:12,959
this isn't a respectable job

553
00:36:14,626 --> 00:36:17,000
and it doesn't pay much.

554
00:36:18,876 --> 00:36:19,999
Yueshan, when you go back,

555
00:36:20,083 --> 00:36:22,000
don't tell your grandma about it.

556
00:36:22,709 --> 00:36:23,709
Why not?

557
00:36:25,999 --> 00:36:27,667
We're family. Why can't I tell her?

558
00:36:29,667 --> 00:36:32,375
Why are you hiding things from us

559
00:36:32,500 --> 00:36:34,667
just because of your pride or dignity?

560
00:36:41,999 --> 00:36:43,999
I'm not a good father

561
00:36:45,999 --> 00:36:47,167
or a good son.

562
00:36:50,334 --> 00:36:51,334
I always said

563
00:36:52,250 --> 00:36:54,125
that I'd bring you to Taipei to live with me

564
00:36:55,250 --> 00:36:56,690
since you were in elementary school.

565
00:36:57,167 --> 00:36:58,999
And look, you're grown up now.

566
00:36:59,000 --> 00:37:00,000
You're in high school.

567
00:37:05,999 --> 00:37:06,999
I'm sorry.

568
00:37:10,209 --> 00:37:11,834
Don't say sorry.

569
00:37:22,999 --> 00:37:24,959
I'm almost done with high school.

570
00:37:28,334 --> 00:37:30,254
When I go to college, I can get a part-time job.

571
00:37:30,999 --> 00:37:33,042
I can take care of myself.

572
00:37:34,375 --> 00:37:35,375
As for Grandma,

573
00:37:35,459 --> 00:37:37,792
she loves selling oysters at the market.

574
00:37:38,751 --> 00:37:40,584
She has many friends in Kinmen.

575
00:37:40,999 --> 00:37:42,292
We're doing well,

576
00:37:46,417 --> 00:37:47,459
but we feel like

577
00:37:49,125 --> 00:37:50,125
the past few years

578
00:37:53,083 --> 00:37:54,203
have been a bit regrettable.

579
00:37:55,959 --> 00:37:57,292
We hardly get to see you

580
00:38:01,999 --> 00:38:03,000
and we miss you a lot.

581
00:38:12,999 --> 00:38:14,167
I miss you both too.

582
00:38:19,292 --> 00:38:21,292
See what a mess I've made of myself?

583
00:38:26,999 --> 00:38:30,209
Your grandma always told me

584
00:38:31,000 --> 00:38:32,999
to stay grounded

585
00:38:33,999 --> 00:38:35,584
and not to aim for instant success.

586
00:38:37,209 --> 00:38:38,959
But I was too greedy.

587
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:40,999
When people told me

588
00:38:41,667 --> 00:38:43,547
investing in the tea business would make money,

589
00:38:43,584 --> 00:38:44,709
I went all in.

590
00:38:45,584 --> 00:38:46,999
In the end, I didn't earn a penny.

591
00:38:48,292 --> 00:38:50,751
Instead, I lost all my savings and ended up in debt.

592
00:38:52,542 --> 00:38:53,626
I...

593
00:38:54,834 --> 00:38:56,999
I'm too ashamed to go back and face everyone.

594
00:39:07,459 --> 00:39:08,459
Yueshan.

595
00:39:18,083 --> 00:39:19,999
Dad, are you building a community here?

596
00:39:23,918 --> 00:39:24,918
Yes.

597
00:39:35,999 --> 00:39:37,542
There seems to be a swimming pool

598
00:39:38,876 --> 00:39:40,751
and a reading room.

599
00:39:45,500 --> 00:39:47,667
There's even a place for karaoke.

600
00:39:48,792 --> 00:39:50,352
The rooftop seems perfect for barbecues

601
00:39:51,959 --> 00:39:53,292
and there's a garden

602
00:39:54,999 --> 00:39:55,999
and a fish pond as well.

603
00:39:57,125 --> 00:39:58,999
I'm sure a lot of people will move in.

604
00:40:03,167 --> 00:40:04,167
My dad

605
00:40:06,959 --> 00:40:10,751
builds warm homes for families.

606
00:40:11,834 --> 00:40:14,417
I'm proud of him.

607
00:40:46,417 --> 00:40:47,417
Yueshan.

608
00:40:51,667 --> 00:40:52,876
From now on,

609
00:40:55,334 --> 00:40:56,999
I'll work hard and stay grounded.

610
00:40:58,500 --> 00:40:59,500
I'll work hard

611
00:41:00,125 --> 00:41:01,125
to pay off the debts

612
00:41:01,751 --> 00:41:04,500
from my tea business investment

613
00:41:05,999 --> 00:41:07,167
and start over.

614
00:41:11,626 --> 00:41:12,626
I hope...

615
00:41:15,709 --> 00:41:16,834
I hope that one day,

616
00:41:19,500 --> 00:41:20,667
our family

617
00:41:23,999 --> 00:41:25,542
can reunite

618
00:41:28,459 --> 00:41:29,751
and live together again.

619
00:41:33,167 --> 00:41:36,542
We could have meals together,

620
00:41:37,709 --> 00:41:38,959
walk by the sea,

621
00:41:39,959 --> 00:41:41,626
and share laughs,

622
00:41:43,999 --> 00:41:46,042
just like other families.

623
00:41:47,083 --> 00:41:48,459
That would be enough.

624
00:41:49,918 --> 00:41:50,918
Okay.

625
00:41:51,250 --> 00:41:52,334
That would be enough.

626
00:41:53,626 --> 00:41:54,626
Okay.

627
00:41:54,999 --> 00:41:56,709
Da, hurry up and get to work!

628
00:41:57,375 --> 00:41:59,417
Okay, I'm coming.

629
00:42:03,042 --> 00:42:04,167
All right, Dad.

630
00:42:04,999 --> 00:42:06,417
You go ahead and work.

631
00:42:06,999 --> 00:42:08,751
I'll head back with Tsai Jingliang.

632
00:42:09,918 --> 00:42:10,918
Okay.

633
00:42:10,999 --> 00:42:11,999
Take care.

634
00:42:11,999 --> 00:42:12,999
Okay.

635
00:42:19,667 --> 00:42:20,834
I forgot something.

636
00:42:21,500 --> 00:42:22,500
What is it?

637
00:42:35,209 --> 00:42:36,542
You can do it, Dad.

638
00:42:39,834 --> 00:42:41,834
I'll do my best in Kinmen too.

639
00:42:42,209 --> 00:42:43,459
Okay, I'll do my best.

640
00:42:44,292 --> 00:42:47,584
Take care of yourself, okay?

641
00:42:51,459 --> 00:42:52,999
If there's anything, let me know.

642
00:42:57,999 --> 00:42:58,999
Bye.

643
00:42:59,000 --> 00:43:00,083
Take care of yourself.

644
00:43:00,999 --> 00:43:01,999
Stay safe on the way.

645
00:43:03,083 --> 00:43:04,083
Bye, Mr. Wang.

646
00:43:04,167 --> 00:43:05,209
Bye.

647
00:43:06,792 --> 00:43:07,992
Let me know when you get home.

648
00:43:08,999 --> 00:43:09,876
Okay.

649
00:43:09,999 --> 00:43:10,999
Bye.

650
00:43:20,751 --> 00:43:21,918
Youtsai.

651
00:43:22,250 --> 00:43:23,542
Has Jingliang contacted you?

652
00:43:23,667 --> 00:43:24,459
No.

653
00:43:24,584 --> 00:43:25,959
He's with Yueshan.

654
00:43:25,999 --> 00:43:27,476
If he contacts me, it would be betraying her.

655
00:43:27,500 --> 00:43:28,292
He wouldn't dare.

656
00:43:28,417 --> 00:43:29,584
You know him well.

657
00:43:30,083 --> 00:43:32,500
There's something I've been meaning to discuss with you.

658
00:43:33,292 --> 00:43:34,292
Look.

659
00:43:35,042 --> 00:43:36,876
The illustrations in this book

660
00:43:36,999 --> 00:43:39,998
may look a bit immature in terms of technique,

661
00:43:39,999 --> 00:43:42,584
but look at the elements they feature.

662
00:43:42,792 --> 00:43:44,667
I think they resemble your style.

663
00:43:45,584 --> 00:43:46,918
As far as I know,

664
00:43:46,999 --> 00:43:49,125
these were drawn by a teenage girl.

665
00:43:49,500 --> 00:43:50,918
The author of this book,

666
00:43:50,999 --> 00:43:51,999
Mr. Ouyang Guangsyong,

667
00:43:52,000 --> 00:43:53,959
really liked her artwork,

668
00:43:53,999 --> 00:43:55,119
so he collected many of them

669
00:43:55,209 --> 00:43:57,169
and decided to use them when publishing the book.

670
00:44:00,500 --> 00:44:02,420
These are all drawings I made when I was little.

671
00:44:03,667 --> 00:44:04,667
Really?

672
00:44:05,709 --> 00:44:08,125
Did you know your drawings were being collected?

673
00:44:09,167 --> 00:44:10,167
I had no idea.

674
00:44:11,999 --> 00:44:14,000
The man you mentioned

675
00:44:14,709 --> 00:44:15,709
is my grandpa.
